        <description><![CDATA[
0 normal open, 1 normal close, 2 switching<br /><h1>Overview</h1><p>Configuaration parameter2 relay type. Default relay type is normal open, only 1 Byte. 0 normal open, 1 normal close, 2 switching</p>
        ]]></description>
